oshi.software.os.windows.nt

Class OSVersionInfoEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • oshi.software.os.windows.nt.OSVersionInfoEx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OperatingSystemVersion

    public class OSVersionInfoEx
extends Object
implements OperatingSystemVersion
    Contains operating system version information. The information includes major and minor version numbers, a build number, a platform identifier, and descriptive text about the operating system.
    Author:
    dblock[at]dblock[dot]org
